      "file_path": "src/test/groovy/org/onap/cps/temporal/repository/NetworkDataRepositorySpec.groovy",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 61,
      "message": "@DataJpaTest takes the control of Transaction and it commits at the end of the test case. It is not suitable in our case as we are validating if the @CreatedTimestamp gets populated in the database and if it happens at the end of the testcase then assert will fail.\n\nhttps://docs.spring.io/spring-boot/docs/current/api/org/springframework/boot/test/autoconfigure/orm/jpa/DataJpaTest.html\n\nTo answer your question, yes we need to add it to end the transaction in the when clause.",
